casebody.data:
Elmore NICHOLS, Jr., Plaintiff,
v.
COURT OF APPEALS, Defendant. SC: 156584 Supreme Court of Michigan. October 26, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the complaint for superintending control is considered and relief is GRANTED in part. We DIRECT the Court of Appeals to docket the plaintiff's June 26, 2017 Motion to Reissue Judgment in Docket No. 333395 as a motion, and to issue an order deciding the motion.

We do not retain jurisdiction.
